25 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code Title 10, Chapter 3, Subchapter 3, is amended
26 to add an additional section to read as follows:
27 10-3-321. Reporting on protection and advocacy for individuals with
28 developmental disabilities.
29 (a) The designated Protection and Advocacy Agency for the state and
30 the designated Client Assistance Program for the state shall:
31 (1) Submit biannual reports to the Hospital, Medicaid, and
32 Developmental Disabilities Study Subcommittee of Legislative Council and the
33 Governor regarding efforts to advocate for all individuals with developmental
34 disabilities who live in a home- and community-based setting and not a
35 facility;
36 (2) Attend meetings of the Hospital, Medicaid, and Developmental
